  phoare[EO_RF(TRF).enc_post : EO_RF.clash_pre ==> EO_RF.clash_pre] = 1%r.
proof.
proc.
if.
seq 2 : (EO_RF.clash_pre).
auto.
auto; progress; by rewrite dtext_ll.
if.
wp; sp; inline*; wp; sp.
if; [auto; progress; by rewrite dtext_ll | auto].
inline*; wp; sp.
if; [auto; progress; by rewrite dtext_ll | auto].
hoare; auto.
trivial.
auto.
qed.

